3. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper involves interference alignment, which is a signal processing technique used to mitigate interference in wireless networks. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper does not directly relate to multimedia, but the K-user interference channel is a common scenario in multimedia communication, where multiple users are transmitting multimedia content simultaneously.
